{"tid":28872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有研究冷戰戰略？","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T09:33:28.000Z","uid":4493,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43fa360be2abfea29f79dfa710e985836d73f06a","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"早排睇完Tom Clancy嘅Red Storm Rising, 又上咗啲討論區睇post, 覺得幾有趣：<br />\n<br />\n- 西德小村莊Fulda一帶叫做Fulda Gap, 係東西德最直接嘅關口。兩邊都住有大量精銳部隊，如果開戰會有幾百架坦克互射，成為世界上最危險嘅地方之一，不過當地居民繼續留低耕田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 英軍嘅柏林旅全部車輛都油上左城市迷彩，適合城市戰但完全唔適合野戰。原因係上頭認為一但開戰，全旅冇生還機會退出市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 近年解密嘅捷克軍事文件包括一個入侵西歐嘅計劃，計劃一開始就會動用戰術核武，一舉將北約趕出歐洲大陸，預計頭七日殺死二千萬平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 一般被人認為最契弟最左派嘅法國其實最熱衷於使用武彈。內部計劃蘇聯一旦攻過萊茵河就會使用戰術武彈，一旦到達法國境內就會用核潛艇同ICBM跟蘇聯同歸於盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 蘇聯嘅T-64坦克推出時性能屈機，西方有七年時間完全無力對付，只好聯手發展下一代主力坦克MBT-70，最後變成M1同豹二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef037cb84587c5a9293c5ebd64a9345cf82ebdab","tid":28872,"uid":14575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"有興趣，留名"},{"pid":"b25d3d07e25da918b063f219c4fd073903f4f94d","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有興趣，留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579922b1a16c7680b2d1b20cc97732c16b69f90a","tid":28872,"uid":10459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"f2ffbcbc2c5e2755cf41dbf4ab4915a9408b085e","tid":28872,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"b06cc97720dc5db2d9399e19a99b5cd27f7eb028","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"比少少時間我會寫多啲"},{"pid":"b9145cbb7b44d740c257b46f03fab053c15cb6a6","tid":28872,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"冷戰熱鬥策略我就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7727227bc7f94eb3c4f34b4a53c59fbec06571b5","tid":28872,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"西史撚留名學野<br />\n<br />\n有少少離題<br />\n其實東西德統一<br />\n東德嘅人係咪普遍存在社會主義思想or價值觀扭曲<br />\n有嘅話係唔係根深蒂固<br />\n佢地會唔會比西德嘅人歧視<br />\n認為東德人係蘇聯統治下嘅怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88e3bf9c347a5e64ffa9243002d54491f481da1","tid":28872,"uid":20158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c445ce2034e278106af53da474761b78fd039ac6","tid":28872,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f068705da39a9f47cd84fe8d8709d4542f225792","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"- 冷戰初期雙方都整左唔少重型坦克，但HEAT嘅普及代表500mm嘅鋼鐵裝甲都抵擋不住，結果大家紛紛改用快速戰車。豹一同AMX-30只能扺擋高射炮！但行到65km/h以上<br />\n至於呢個戰術有冇效，要到1991年先由法軍在伊拉克證實係OK的，AMX30車隊打敗更先進厚甲T-72。"},{"pid":"8b51faf3073785ac8c27f57862cd0c39f0039c19","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西史撚留名學野<br />\n<br />\n有少少離題<br />\n其實東西德統一<br />\n東德嘅人係咪普遍存在社會主義思想or價值觀扭曲<br />\n有嘅話係唔係根深蒂固<br />\n佢地會唔會比西德嘅人歧視<br />\n認為東德人係蘇聯統治下嘅怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n優秀嘅東德人比中國人更早睇穿社會主義嘅失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到七十年代中已經個個諗住點逃走，到九十年代自願接受資本主義。"},{"pid":"2e27faa7d99a57ac73c0293001c1d8fc5c49b27b","tid":28872,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53671d57920b8f199574c15b810810b7c1b7042d","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:10:09.000Z","msg":"- 1965-1975年之間，西方各國嘅坦克各有千秋。有坦克兵話：英國酋長嘅裝甲，德國豹一嘅引擎，法國嘅火砲加上美國嘅電子系統就係一部完美嘅坦克。<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n- 酋長嘅細角度傾斜裝甲可以有效彈開砲彈，或者減低彈頭穿甲作用。唯一正面頂到115mm砲彈攻擊。<br />\n- 豹一個引擎無論加速同埋極速都好快，更加係最可靠同容易拆出來維修。平均維護時間係酋長三分人。<br />\n- 法國AMX-30的105mm砲比NATO標準L7砲更長，威力更大。酋長的120mm雖然動能更大，但法國的Obus G特殊穿甲彈可以貫穿500mm裝甲，一發價值等於當年一部全新私家車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 美國係第一國裝備激光測距火控系統，無線電等都係最先進，加上設計方便使用。"},{"pid":"25589dca2326f02203a49b3d8482599e475e2e0d","tid":28872,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0b38a8de8fa781931f0a1ace7a83a16952eca7","tid":28872,"uid":55417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"留名學野  樓主繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92f573a4f1e9c0a38c7ec37d6fb6de446fede5d","tid":28872,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"其實冷戰戰略唔係就係icbm+核武咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f361c48cf9e0727f393f954f39929738bfb6bbac","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實冷戰戰略唔係就係icbm+核武咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全面戰爭就係，但雙方其實都寧可打常規或者加少量戰術核武，打到對方講和賠償。<br />\n聯共華約最想食埋東德同北歐，搶資源救經濟。"},{"pid":"19ea26d78ef8c88b051bf27522ae5e26dd620467","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實冷戰戰略唔係就係icbm+核武咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全面戰爭就係，但雙方其實都寧可打常規或者加少量戰術核武，打到對方講和賠償。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘇共</span>華約最想食埋東德同北歐，搶資源救經濟。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"981bed5ffdcd6e2f4492f361b17660de73d00502","tid":28872,"uid":33045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e4f67bea6099778832f480bf35233821b25b93f9","tid":28872,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7574b2e56ee7f16b733b706c809b7784474daa0f","tid":28872,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b382e65d9dd3129e1fe9f9e4755523508552e73e","tid":28872,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f5a0ee94010eba9f26c65ea9fa4d18a0f5e9a7","tid":28872,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"好中意睇冷戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d4dc643fcee69f56026f99117571bd62383dd5","tid":28872,"uid":54012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7546ac5842fb0b9256742897dda32d2751e1b748","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8c0c7fe59e9df3efafbb58cc0401b26124db36","tid":28872,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰空差異"},{"pid":"1b5b43b01bed366b7c340afa4e9a6527df32723d","tid":28872,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰空軍差異</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f1464a39093c7b84122a3aaedb92e266a1115b4","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰空軍差異</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰蘇聯最強嘅係米格十五，配上精英蘇聯機師，初期打殘英美軍，迫美國要出動F-86配上頂級機師先至打成平手。<br />\n<br />\n米格十五機身設計好好，係用納粹德國嘅設計加上俄羅斯自己科學家嘅改良做到，一直冇適合嘅噴射引擎，後來英國勞斯萊斯on99開放比蘇聯官員參觀，其中一個間諜偷到金屬碎片，先至抄到Nene嘅設計。<br />\n<br />\n斯太林年代蘇聯用盡錢研究武器，終於在1965年左右追到西方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e048e6b52b94341592d59de2ce5ac321cc52c0","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"上面提過嘅法國Obus G炮彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8L9QHyq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8L9QHyq.jpg&h=6b216baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設計極度複雜，一粒價值今日$25萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但除非目標有複合裝甲，否則一打中保證一發入魂，極高溫嘅金屬碎片係類似等離子狀態之下在車內亂飛，將裏面嘅士兵射死燒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcfea2c9201d7b97b7c8736d01a6f97afb733ba","tid":28872,"uid":59626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b6a192a9e0a10738156686bbff210bde194bd629","tid":28872,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"識嘢"},{"pid":"e156700307b4e7401bc682173a462b8a2e26a0b2","tid":28872,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"仲以為同條女冷戰<br />\n我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8441bd532ff7874e22afa244c4662902ec593715","tid":28872,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n45係最佳宣戰時機<br />\n首先得美國有原子彈<br />\n其次蘇聯由鋁合金到罐頭到鐵路系統都依靠lend lease<br />\n再者就係柏林戰役消耗左蘇軍大量既兵力同進攻能量<br />\n<br />\n當時英國有個&ldquo;不可思議計劃&rdquo;就係"},{"pid":"ab93288fc50c64dc6b877cbda4855bb575ca01f9","tid":28872,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西史撚留名學野<br />\n<br />\n有少少離題<br />\n其實東西德統一<br />\n東德嘅人係咪普遍存在社會主義思想or價值觀扭曲<br />\n有嘅話係唔係根深蒂固<br />\n佢地會唔會比西德嘅人歧視<br />\n認為東德人係蘇聯統治下嘅怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東德人本身其實係成個東歐生活水準最高個批來<br />\n統一之後突然間感受到西德比自己發達好多，本身做專業人士既個群證書又唔認可，淪落到去左保安或者運輸，呢批人係受到最大影響，東德支持舊體制既主要係呢批人<br />\n底下階層個批反而影響不大，德國仲有個統一稅由西德出錢養起每個東德人，享受同西德同等既福利制度（無錯，西德憲法講明德國是民主社會主義國家）<br />\n最大影響其實係西德既開放移民/多元文化政策，引入左大批外國人同東德競爭，變相令東德人偏向排外，撒克森州，前波爾曼尼亞州明顯比西德右傾，德累斯頓仲係右翼大本營，西德比較左膠就覺得東德班人好新納粹好法西斯<br />\n<br />\n其實東西統一之前，兩個人民既交流已經好多，80年代好多西德人已經可以去東德探親，東德人無得四圍走但已經可以收到西德電視台電台信號，或者由親友個度收到西方產品，唔係好似南北韓個種完全隔離既狀態"},{"pid":"1c4632b5698ba8394f640cbf157cf6da55595e9d","tid":28872,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰空軍差異</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰蘇聯最強嘅係米格十五，配上精英蘇聯機師，初期打殘英美軍，迫美國要出動F-86配上頂級機師先至打成平手。<br />\n<br />\n米格十五機身設計好好，係用納粹德國嘅設計加上俄羅斯自己科學家嘅改良做到，一直冇適合嘅噴射引擎，後來英國勞斯萊斯on99開放比蘇聯官員參觀，其中一個間諜偷到金屬碎片，先至抄到Nene嘅設計。<br />\n<br />\n斯太林年代蘇聯用盡錢研究武器，終於在1965年左右追到西方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機師Ar I mean<br />\n15 engine好似係工黨送"},{"pid":"b768de0b804d3caa47afb2025e5730b6e2fa5301","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n45係最佳宣戰時機<br />\n首先得美國有原子彈<br />\n其次蘇聯由鋁合金到罐頭到鐵路系統都依靠lend lease<br />\n再者就係柏林戰役消耗左蘇軍大量既兵力同進攻能量<br />\n<br />\n當時英國有個&ldquo;不可思議計劃&rdquo;就係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOperation Unthinkable.<br />\n問題係以當時製造速度 要三到五個月先整到一個原子彈 加上喺宣傳角度用咗唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返冷戰 柏林大空運期間都好緊張 當時西方好有把握打得贏"},{"pid":"0edf40fcf94bf70e12339d8c87a88cc4020f2885","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"蘇聯T-64坦克初期型<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/205914_202559336228de1cecb00d6f921afbb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F205914_202559336228de1cecb00d6f921afbb7.jpg&h=1fed52a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 因為復合裝甲極度屈機，火砲威力世界第一 (用T-62 115mm一樣嘅彈頭，但係更加多推進藥)，一度令西方震驚，北約認為用現役坦克至少要三打一先有機會贏。正面只有反坦克導彈可以打穿。<br />\n實際上T-64成本極高，並不可靠，結果只生產左少數，主力由比較輕便嘅T-72擔任。<br />\n<br />\n現代複合裝甲，T-64都係類似設計。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10Gvz54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10Gvz54.jpg&h=b238f7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 如果冷戰爆發，數量不多嘅T-64好可能第一個星期已經全部消滅，之後就靠生產左幾萬部嘅T-55補上。西方大部份嘅坦克足夠應付T-55。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kczs3t1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKczs3t1.jpg&h=26576b32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e98436d8c052382752129e599f49680ea2aa3e","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0766a3252ab6256652980b543f204bcbaa599afd","tid":28872,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"留明學嘢"},{"pid":"bbd85504149eb00bb8ec02a80b2534e29864f33d","tid":28872,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"07d951939c4c3988e3d185565d23efc4cb789fc1","tid":28872,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰空軍差異</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓戰蘇聯最強嘅係米格十五，配上精英蘇聯機師，初期打殘英美軍，迫美國要出動F-86配上頂級機師先至打成平手。<br />\n<br />\n米格十五機身設計好好，係用納粹德國嘅設計加上俄羅斯自己科學家嘅改良做到，一直冇適合嘅噴射引擎，後來英國勞斯萊斯on99開放比蘇聯官員參觀，其中一個間諜偷到金屬碎片，先至抄到Nene嘅設計。<br />\n<br />\n斯太林年代蘇聯用盡錢研究武器，終於在1965年左右追到西方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機師Ar I mean<br />\n15 engine好似係工黨送</blockquote><br />\nyes 工黨左膠一向都要死全家"},{"pid":"28a4eec77470a202e1f9528bcb020841ae9b3ac5","tid":28872,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果淨計1945至1955 除左用原子彈核平之外應該冇方法擋到紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過會污染埋北歐同氣化埋北約前線軍人<br />\n<br />\n 熱血紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大縱深戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西方盟軍喺知道有原子彈之前已經有計劃，要由美國增兵同考慮用十萬投降德兵同德軍裝備進攻，最大問題係要說服國民支持打蘇聯呢個盟友。<br />\n<br />\nUSSR 1945年軍備充足，但食物燃料仍然極靠美國。停lend-lease半年，紅軍已經無油無罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n參加過二戰嘅紅軍士兵，八成在1941-1945年之間戰死，蘇聯有世代斷層，即1945年夠16歲的男人已經唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n45係最佳宣戰時機<br />\n首先得美國有原子彈<br />\n其次蘇聯由鋁合金到罐頭到鐵路系統都依靠lend lease<br />\n再者就係柏林戰役消耗左蘇軍大量既兵力同進攻能量<br />\n<br />\n當時英國有個&ldquo;不可思議計劃&rdquo;就係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOperation Unthinkable.<br />\n問題係以當時製造速度 要三到五個月先整到一個原子彈 加上喺宣傳角度用咗唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返冷戰 柏林大空運期間都好緊張 當時西方好有把握打得贏</blockquote><br />\n美國當時（1已有10或以上既粒庫存"},{"pid":"ee4c3a6c2fa2ba8da487ec991cd1a5dc1eabdf04","tid":28872,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"mutual assured destruction呢個諗法都幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名學野"},{"pid":"cf5a1639a64581f1f42a533f8246d8babcb6a522","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mutual assured destruction呢個諗法都幾誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名學野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽落去好似好恐怖 但其實係最安全<br />\n歐洲冷戰年代好似係幾個世紀以來最和平 後果太大就冇人敢搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n博弈論同埋零和遊戲都同佢有關 有興趣可以睇吓電影 「Wargame」。<br />\n<br />\n另外講到人性 就算係訓練最有素嘅軍人 - 美國ICBM兵，喺一個突擊測試裏面都有四份一人拒絕接受命令發射核彈。但呢個比例其實比科學家原先估計低咗。"},{"pid":"8bdbdbc23478e9d87807cb4b93476ef1f89ae9a3","tid":28872,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"eb8225fe8bfe66e676a0db55ae8abc1c2def928e","tid":28872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1a5b5afdbccb08be761f92063b60621979090e","tid":28872,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01c5854e3bf85ba4aa0459e38ad885a72f64221f","tid":28872,"uid":25329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"Hist jj lm"},{"pid":"f410a031446c859e9974b144431ca16c77b76392","tid":28872,"uid":55311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學嘢<br />\n樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlearn"},{"pid":"e7c04e0e1db000993534909eed477ab9a4dee6a5","tid":28872,"uid":3966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果nazi早D有stg44有冇可能打嬴USSR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1247512c406fd059f2a941759d3617714988d8cb","tid":28872,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果nazi早D有stg44有冇可能打嬴USSR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一支自動步槍改變到d咩...<br />\n蘇聯火炮空軍坦克人數都多至少一倍...<br />\n後期真係無得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠都係大炮轟炸 空襲 再坦克配步兵一線平推"},{"pid":"fd95e24e7f5a4bcff699b97d5ba9579dcd085976","tid":28872,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果nazi早D有stg44有冇可能打嬴USSR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNo a gun cannot save anything without ammo and holder he177 is more important"},{"pid":"0f428983f4077b60a4b36a4fbf83f0e304040b35","tid":28872,"uid":15863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d21859d6239f154ccdd2b82ccdc6f5b0b6182e9","tid":28872,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:40:54.000Z","msg":"講冷戰其實值得一提既係Able Archer 83演習，當時蘇聯真係認爲北約打算發動第一波核打擊，蘇聯波蘭東德既核武部隊都進入高度警戒，而美國幾乎完全唔知情&middot;<br />\n<br />\n除左古巴導彈危機之外，Able Archer 83應該是世界最接近核戰既一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa2a026b87a3a66d3a48dcc325cc25fa59edf69","tid":28872,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T22:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果nazi早D有stg44有冇可能打嬴USSR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一支自動步槍改變到d咩...<br />\n蘇聯火炮空軍坦克人數都多至少一倍...<br />\n後期真係無得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠都係大炮轟炸 空襲 再坦克配步兵一線平推</blockquote><br />\n德軍唔係輸人數裝備，係輸希特拉d on9戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416029eab4758501d6d2e73db56b080a22ee8063","tid":28872,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T22:25:58.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"39b49f4b7f9